How to game zoom it is very long fix a zoom 

If your game screen is too zoomed in or too zoomed out, you can fix the zoom in a few common ways depending on how you are making the game. 🎮

1. Fix Zoom Using Camera Size
Most games control zoom with the camera.

Open your Camera settings in the game engine.

Change Field of View (FOV) or Camera Size.

Bigger value → more zoomed out

Smaller value → more zoomed in

Example idea:

FOV = 60 → normal zoom

FOV = 80–90 → more zoom out

2. Fix Zoom for Mobile Games
If you are making a mobile game:

Set a fixed camera position

Lock the zoom so players cannot change it

Example logic:

camera.zoom = 1.0
camera.lock = true
3. Fix Zoom With Screen Resolution
Sometimes the zoom problem happens because of wrong resolution.

Try:

Set game resolution like 1920×1080 (PC)

Or 1280×720 (mobile)

4. If You Are Using a Game Maker App on Phone
Many mobile game maker apps have:

Camera Zoom

Viewport scale

Set:

Zoom = 1

Viewport = Fit Screen

