Human of last of us walk scrypt

If you want a human walking script like in The Last of Us, you need a player movement script that moves the character in 4 directions and plays a walk animation. 🚶‍♂️🎮

Simple Human Walk Script
Example basic movement:

speed = 3

if (input.left) {
    player.x -= speed
}

if (input.right) {
    player.x += speed
}

if (input.up) {
    player.y -= speed
}

if (input.down) {
    player.y += speed
}
Walk Animation Script
To make the character walk animation play:

if (player.moving) {
    player.animation = "walk"
} else {
    player.animation = "idle"
}
Sprint (Run) Script
Like survival games:

if (input.sprint) {
    speed = 6
} else {
    speed = 3
}
This will give:

Normal walking

Running (sprint)

Idle animation

✅ This creates a basic human movement system similar to survival games like The Last of Us Part I.

