Create a game of last of us survival game code

You cannot copy the exact game The Last of Us because it belongs to Naughty Dog, but you can make a similar survival game with basic code. 🎮

Below is a simple survival game example (player movement + health + shooting + enemies).

1. Player Movement Code
This lets the human character walk.

let speed = 3;

if (input.left) {
  player.x -= speed;
}

if (input.right) {
  player.x += speed;
}

if (input.up) {
  player.y -= speed;
}

if (input.down) {
  player.y += speed;
}
2. Sprint System
Player runs faster.

if (input.sprint) {
  speed = 6;
} else {
  speed = 3;
}
3. Shooting System
Player shoots enemies.

if (input.shoot) {
  spawn("bullet", player.x, player.y);
}
Bullet movement:

bullet.x += bullet.speed;
4. Enemy (Zombie) AI
Enemies follow the player.

let dx = player.x - enemy.x;
let dy = player.y - enemy.y;

enemy.x += dx * 0.02;
enemy.y += dy * 0.02;
5. Health System
Player loses health when enemy touches.

if (player.collide(enemy)) {
  player.health -= 10;
}
6. Camera Follow
Camera follows the player.

camera.follow(player);
camera.zoom = 1.8;
